						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in the tank bed to the north of Baṭṭupalle.</p>						

						<p>Kāyastha, Ambadēva: 1290 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1212, Vikṛita, Bhādrapada, śu. 5, Thursday,</hi> corresponding to 1290 A.D., August 12. The weekday, however was Saturday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It seems to record the construction of the tank at Rāvulakolanu by Mahāpradhāni Goḍerāya Gaṅgidēvaya.</p>						

						</summary>
